title: Being Excellent in the Workplace | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Being Excellent in the Workplace | Joel Osteen
description:
Whatever we do, we should do to the best of our ability. When you strive to work with excellence every day, you are honoring God with your faithfulness.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
